md:
giải nghĩa từ "iii" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

iii (pronoun)

* Meaning: he/she/it (used as a pronoun to refer to a person or thing)
* Type: pronoun
* Example sentence: "He is going to the store." (Here, "he" is used as a pronoun to refer to a person.)
* Related words: he, she, it, they
* Antonyms: you, I, we

iii (Roman numeral)

* Meaning: three
* Type: numeral
* Example sentence: "The Roman numeral iii represents the number three." (Here, "iii" is used as a Roman numeral to represent the number three.)
* Related words: i, ii, iv, v
* Antonyms: none

Note: The meaning of "iii" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. In the first example, it is used as a pronoun, while in the second example, it is used as a Roman numeral.
